name: Say Her Name
description:
I have died many times of bow,
Dull,Dark,Silent.
Eyes are deep pools
of esoteric history.
Say her name,
They whisper of tantalizing magic
secrets and mysteries.
Say her name,
They speak of crippling defeats
abuse, deceits and trickery;
of allowing herself to be used as nothing
more than an accessory.
Say her name,
But also hard won and fought for victories
and bare naked authenticity.
